					<note><hi rend="bold">Colophon further notes:</hi> The final page (on different paper in a different hand)  bears a chronogram for the date 1054. If the title اخلاق پادشاهى is a chronogram, the associated date is 1055, which Ethé took to be the date of composition.</note>
					<note>
						<hi rend="bold">Note concerning work: </hi>A work on <foreign>adab</foreign> (ethics) for rulers. Very likely the same work as in <ref target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_6120#Or_6694-item2">BL Or. 6694/2</ref> (same title, same date of composition, 1055/1645-6).
